00:37:43.290 --> 00:37:48.350
This is magnitude
of oscillations

00:37:48.350 --> 00:37:52.020
of the first element.

00:37:52.020 --> 00:37:53.610
And you can do the
same thing for B2.

00:38:02.020 --> 00:38:04.080
And I'm not trying
