00:40:23.370 --> 00:40:31.650
and I have k over m plus
g over l minus omega

00:40:31.650 --> 00:40:36.910
d squared over k over m.

00:40:40.190 --> 00:40:42.470
And-- yeah.

00:40:42.470 --> 00:40:47.270
